snippet.title: E! News
snippet.description:
E! News is the modern-and-bold mood for the pop cultured – brought to life by the diverse perspectives viewers can connect with, in addition to unexpected takes & plenty of laughs! It’s a fun, fresh spin on celebrity news. The show and its hosts have an edgy, exciting vibe and will bring you the stories you and your friends won’t stop talking about. E! News will feature A-list interviews, rising stars, and pop culture exclusives you won’t find anywhere else!

Watch your favorite dramas, comedies, true crime and reality, plus news, sports and pop culture updates on Peacock, the new streaming service from NBCUniversal. Stream now. https://bit.ly/PeacockE
